"zebra-dove":{n:"Zebra Dove",c:"Bird",s:"Dove",sz:"Small",cl:"Brown & White",i:"ğŸ¦",wp:"Zebra_dove",d:"A small, delicate dove with soft brown plumage and distinctive fine black barring on the neck, breast, and flanks giving a zebra-striped appearance. Native to Southeast Asia but widely introduced elsewhere. Highly valued in Southeast Asian cultures for their melodious cooing. Often seen feeding calmly on the ground.",w:"40-60 g",l:"20-23 cm",life:"10-15 years",act:"Diurnal",diet:"Granivore â€” small seeds, grain",cs:"Least Concern"},
